# 🚀 VNPT Workflow Slash Command Handler

> **Variables:** This file uses `{{VARIABLE}}` tokens resolved from `_project_config.mdc`.
> When copying to a new project: update `_project_config.mdc` only.
>
> **⚠️ TRIGGER ĐIỀU KIỆN** — Rule này CHỈ active khi user prompt có `/vnpt_workflow_*`.

---

## 🤖 AGENT CONFIGURATION (Model per Stage)

```yaml
agents:
  dev:
    model: composer-2.5-fast
    temperature: 0.5

  review:
    model: claude-4.6
    temperature: 0.1

  fix:
    model: claude-4.6
    temperature: 0.2
```

