## ⛔ HARD RULES (BẮT BUỘC — KHÔNG ĐƯỢC VI PHẠM)

> Variables: `{{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}}`, `{{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}`, `{{PROVIDER_BASE}}`, `{{CONSUMER_BASE}}`, `{{BRAND}}`, `{{I18N_CLASS}}`, `{{STATE_TYPE}}`, `{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}`, `{{M_SHOW_TOAST}}`, `{{M_SHOW_LOADING}}`.

### Rule 1: LUÔN dùng `{{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}`, KHÔNG dùng `Scaffold` trực tiếp

```dart
// ❌ SAI — KHÔNG dùng Scaffold
return Scaffold(
  backgroundColor: ColorApp.backgroundDefault,
  appBar: AppBar(
    title: Text({{I18N_CLASS}}.title),
  ),
  body: ProgressHUD(
    child: {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(...),
  ),
);

// ✅ ĐÚNG — {{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}} wrap sẵn ProgressHUD + AppBar + SafeArea
class XxxScreen extends {{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}} {
  const XxxScreen({super.key});
  @override
  State<XxxScreen> createState() => _XxxScreenState();
}

class _XxxScreenState
    extends {{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}<XxxScreen, XxxService, XxxProvider> {
  @override
  Widget buildBody(BuildContext context) {
    return {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(...);
  }
}
```

`{{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}` handles:
- `initState()` → `{{INIT_EVENT_LISTENER}}` (wires eventStream) + `Connectivity` listener.
- `dispose()` → cancels subscription.
- `build()` → `buildRoot(context)` → `{{CONSUMER_BASE}}` (auto-switches on `currentState`).

### Rule 2: Body Widget KHÔNG chứa `Scaffold` / `AppBar` / `ProgressHUD`

```dart
// ❌ SAI — Body bị bọc lại ProgressHUD/AppBar ({{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}} đã có)
class BodyXxxWidget extends StatefulWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      appBar: AppBar(...),       // ❌
      body: ProgressHUD(          // ❌
        child: {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(...),
      ),
    );
  }
}

// ✅ ĐÚNG — Body chỉ chứa content
class BodyXxxWidget extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(
      onRepositorySuccess: (repo) => _buildContent(repo as XxxProvider),
    );
  }
}
```

